    "description": "YRGLM Inc. engages in the marketing and commerce AI business primarily in Japan. It operates Ad Ebis, an advertising effectiveness measurement platform that supports decision-making with accurate data; AD EBiS Campaign Manager, a marketing campaign management platform; CAPiCO, a conversion API tool, which helps to improve the accuracy of measuring conversion data for various advertising medium; and TargetPush, a web push notification tool. The company also offers automatic reporting tool for performance-based advertising; AdHoop, a web marketing specialized matching solution; and creative agency and SNS marketing services. In addition, it provides EC-CUBE, an e-commerce open platform; e-commerce fulfilment services; and Redmine, a cloud service for the open-source project management software. The company was formerly known as LOCKON Co., LTD. and changed its name to YRGLM Inc. in August 2019. YRGLM Inc. was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
